OP06-OP06-022 normal.name: Yamato (OP06-022)
OP06-OP06-022 normal.description:
[Double Attack] (This card deals 2 damage.)
[Activate:Main] [Once Per Turn] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, give up to 2 rested DON!! cards to 1 of your Characters.

OP06-OP06-100 normal.name: Inuarashi (Reprint)
OP06-OP06-100 normal.description:
[DON!! x2][When Attacking] You may trash 1 card from your hand: K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost equal to or less than the number of your opponent's Life cards.
[Trigger] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, play this card.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP06 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP06-OP06-103 normal.name: Kawamatsu (Reprint)
OP06-OP06-103 normal.description:
[When Attacking] You may trash 2 cards from your hand: Add up to 1 of your Characters with 0 power to the top or bottom of the owner's Life cards face-up.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP06 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP06-OP06-104 normal.name: Kikunojo (Reprint)
OP06-OP06-104 normal.description:
[On K.O.] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, add up to 1 card from the top of your deck to the top of your Life cards.
[Trigger] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, play this card.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP06 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP06-OP06-109 normal.name: Denjiro (Reprint)
OP06-OP06-109 normal.description:
[DON!! x2] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, this Character cannot be K.O.'d by effects.
[Trigger] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, play this card.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP06 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP06-OP06-110 normal.name: Nekomamushi (Reprint)
OP06-OP06-110 normal.description:
[DON!! x2] This Character can also attack your opponent's active Characters.
[Trigger] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, play this card.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP06 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP06-OP06-112 normal.name: Raizo (Reprint)
OP06-OP06-112 normal.description:
[When Attacking] You may trash 1 card from your hand: Rest up to 1 of your opponent's DON!! cards.
[Trigger] If your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, play this card.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP06 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP07-OP07-116 normal.name: Blaze Slice (Reprint)
OP07-OP07-116 normal.description:
[Main] / [Counter] Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +1000 power during this turn. Then, if your opponent has 2 or less Life cards, rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 4 or less.
[Trigger] Rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 4 or less.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP07 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

OP09-OP09-035 normal.name: Portgas.D.Ace (Reprint)
OP09-OP09-035 normal.description:
[On Play] If you have 2 or more rested Characters, rest up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 5 or less.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the OP09 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

ST13-ST13-016 normal.name: Yamato (Reprint)
ST13-ST13-016 normal.description:
[Rush] (This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)
[On Play] Look at all your Life cards; place 1 at the top of your deck and place the rest back in your Life area in any order.

DISCLAIMER: This card is a reprint of the pre-existing card in the ST13 set. The main difference between this card and the original print is the inclusion of "EN" on the right side, by the copyright information.

ST28-ST28-001 normal.name: Ashura Doji
ST28-ST28-001 normal.description: [On Play] If your Leader has the "Land of Wano" type and your opponent has 3 or more Life cards, K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a base cost of 5 or less.

ST28-ST28-002 normal.name: Izo
ST28-ST28-002 normal.description:
[DON!! x2] This Character gains [Blocker].
[On Play] Your "Land of Wano" type Leader gains [Banish] during this turn.

ST28-ST28-003 normal.name: Kin'emon
ST28-ST28-003 normal.description: [Trigger] If your Leader has the "Land of Wano" type and your opponent has 3 or less Life cards, play this card.

ST28-ST28-004 normal.name: Kouzuki Momonosuke
ST28-ST28-004 normal.description:
[Your Turn] If you have 2 or less Life cards, your Leader gains +1000 power.
[Activate: Main] [Once Per Turn] You may return 2 total of your currently given DON!! cards to your cost area rested: This Character gains [Rush] and +1000 power during this turn.
(This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)

ST28-ST28-005 normal.name: Yamato
ST28-ST28-005 normal.description:
[DON!! x2] [Your Turn] This Character gains +3000 power.
[On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 "Land of Wano" type card with a cost of 2 or more and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.
